LOCATION:Fringe Boulevard\, King William St (between James St N and Hughson
  St N)\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: Keeping Six (Hamilton)\nGenre: Free Outdoor Events\nKe
 eping Six Hamilton is the Hamilton Harm Reduction Action League that defen
 ds the rights\, dignity and humanity of people who are struggling with add
 iction. Keeping Six Open Mic Night is an evening that provides members of 
 the K6 community the platform to share their writings and lived experience
  to an audience.\nGeneral Admission: FREE\nMore info: https://hftco.ca/eve
 nts/keeping-six-open-mic-presented-by-hamilton-community-foundation/
