SUMMARY:Interactive Hand Drum Circle W/ Auntie Social Singers
LOCATION:Fringe Boulevard\, King William St (between James St N and Hughson
  St N)\, Hamilton\, ON
DESCRIPTION:Company: HFTco (Hamilton)\nGenre: Free Outdoor Events\, Family 
 Programming\nJoin Tammy for an interactive drum circle. A brief overview o
 f the four sacred medicines will be introduced along with the singing of c
 ultural songs and teachings. Tammy is a drum carrier with Mohawk roots (Mo
 ntreal\, Quebec) as well as French\, Irish and Scottish. She is an active 
 member of the urban Indigenous community in the Niagara Region and is retu
 rning for her second year on Fringe Boulevard.\nGeneral Admission: FREE\nM
 ore info: https://hftco.ca/events/interactive-hand-drum-circle-w-auntie-so
 cial-singers/
